    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. The CFD model predicts RH < 1.0 across all five operating points, satisfying the regulatory acceptance criterion. Validation agreement metrics (NRMSE = 0.08, R² = 0.91) against the Thamsen et al. reference dataset are within acceptable bounds. The pressure-head validation against the FDA PIV dataset further supports hydraulic fidelity. The credibility evidence is assessed as sufficient to support the claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device at MRL 2. Decision: Accepted.",
